<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style_rpage.css"/>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <title>shree shanta hostel management systems</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar">
                <div class="navbar_college" >
                    <img height="70" width="190" src="./assets/banasthali_vidyapith_logo.jpeg" alt="logo" class="college_logo"/>
                </div>
                <div class="navbar_nav_items">
                    <div class="nav_item_1">
                        <button class="button__primary_1"><a href="">My Profile</a></button>
                        <button class="button__primary_1"><a href="">Home</a></button>
                        <button class="button__primary"><a href=""> About us</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main class="container">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="content_text">
                  <h3>
                 As you navigate this new chapter, keep your door open, metaphorically and literally. Be open to new friendships, experiences, and ideas. Your room isn't just a private space;<br>
                  it's a part of a larger community that is eager to welcome you with open arms.
                </h3> 
            </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hero_icons">
               <div class="icon_text"> How Does It Work</div>
                <div class="icon1_text">
                    <img height="250px" width="230px" src="assets/icon1.gif" alt="icon1" class="icon_1">
                    <div class="text1"><h3>First Come First Serve</h3></div>
                </div>
                <div class="icon2_text">
                    <img height="250px" width="230px" src="assets/icon2.gif" alt="icon2" class="icon_1">
                    <div class="text1"><h3>The Early Birds Catches The Worm</h3></div>
                </div>
                <div class="icon3_text">
                    <img height="250px" width="230px" src="assets/icon4.gif" alt="icon4" class="icon_1">
                    <div class="text1"><h3>  Rooms In Sharing</h3></div>
                </div>
                <div class="icon4_text">
                    <img height="250px" width="230px" src="assets/icon3.gif" alt="icon3" class="icon_1">
                    <div class="text1"><h3> Confirm Your Room</h3></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hero">
                <div class="hero_text">
                <h3><i>
                To simplify your booking process, we have provided a detailed table showcasing the availability of our rooms.
                Rooms are allocated on a first-come, first-served basis Explore the table, select the room that suits your preferences,
                and secure your spot for an amazing year please proceed to fill out the form indicating your chosen dates and room preferences.
                </i></h3>
                </div>
              </div>
            <div class="room_container">
            <div class="form">
            <form class="form_container" action="/student-module/index_rpage.ejs/submit" method="post">
            <h2>
            <label for="hostel">Hostel Name(ex. gram):</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="hostel" name="hostel" required><br>

            <!-- <label for="student_id">Student Id:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="student_id" name="student_id" required><br> -->

            <label for="room_num">Room number:</label><br>
            <input type="number" id="room_num" name="room_num" required><br>

            <button class="button__primary_3" type="submit">Submit</button><br>
            </h2>
            </form>
        </div>
            </div>
            <style>
                table {
                    border-collapse: collapse;
                    margin-left: 45%;
                    margin-top: -30%;
                    width: 50%;
                }
                th, td {
                    border: 1px solid black;
                    padding: 8px;
                    text-align: left;
                }
                th {
                    background-color: #f2f2f2;
                }
                avail{
                    margin-left: 45%;
                    margin-top: -30%;
                }
            </style>
        </head>
        <body>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Room No</th>
                        <th>Floor</th>
                        <th>Vacancy</th>
                        <!-- Add more table headers if needed -->
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% data.forEach(item => { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= item.room_no %></td>
                            <td><%= item.floor_no %></td>
                            <td><%= item.vaccant %></td>
                            <!-- <td><%= item.detail_new %>  </td> -->
                            <!-- Add more table data if needed -->
                        </tr>
                    <% }); %>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
        


